        definition
            statement: p
                | #[m \Lambda ] is a lattice if it is a rank 2 #[m \ZZ]-module in #[m \CC] s.t. #[m \CC/\Lambda ] is compact.
                me \Lambda = \tau _1\ZZ + \tau _2 \ZZ
